	   <tr><td colspan=2>You crazy old coot, Pusbag!&nbsp;&nbsp;So that's why Iksar Shamans keep on trying to pull this dwarf into the Lake of Ill Omen.  Lucky for me I resist many of their DD or DOT's, or I just back off and heal while I wait for them to come out of the water.  Just the other day an Iksar asked me why I didn't chase him into the water.  Of course I am a dwarf so I didn't answer him, but I did take another swing at him.<br><br>Ironhom Hammerforge<br>Dwarven Paladin<br>Tallon Zek Server<br>&nbsp;<br>Judd Jaggedoak <br>(deceased)<br>Wood Elf Ranger<br><br><br><br><br></td></tr>
